data.text:
Maria Borges (born 28 October 1992, Luanda) is an Angolan fashion model. She was named Forbes Africa Magazine's top model of 2013. She is a Riccardo Tisci favorite and calls him her "godfather". Maria Borges made history on 10 November 2015 by being the first black model to ever walk in the Victoria's Secret fashion show whilst wearing her natural afro hair.
